{"tid":1198642,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"CNN:  香港69遊行參與者比「雨傘革命」廣泛得多,  林鄭可能時日無多","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T13:40:17.000Z","uid":134071,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"127e5a5e262b6fd5bb75b1f70328af0e5e857834","tid":1198642,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:47:08.000Z","msg":"(AM730翻譯)<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡(CNN)則刊出分析文章，指本港的抗議行動本來已在「吊命」(was on life support)，但政府卻令它「復甦」，指相較於由學生主導的傘運，今次參與「反送中」示威的民眾層面廣泛得多，有律師、商人及中產人士參加，也有不少首次參加抗議行動的中年人。文章認為，特首林鄭月娥「可能時日無多」(Lam's days may be numbered)，指她應該不會辭職，但北京可能會在她完成任期後，另覓繼任人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://edition.cnn.com/2019/06/10/asia/hong-kong-extradition-protest-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-extradition-protest-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=AePTNAtL1N4PdcNq2S6jCNOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=ecdc8d70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F06%2F10%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-extradition-protest-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=d6181d73\" target=\"_blank\">http://edition.cnn.com/2019/06/10/asia/hong-kong-extradition-protest-intl-hnk/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"fd74b399983d05a0307efc8f01b15f0c31a4d3d7","tid":1198642,"uid":99607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"搞到佢年老唔過得世 應該係大眾人都可希望既"},{"pid":"d4cb143c1e90f9cefcd1c0c9fc26440a8f006fae","tid":1198642,"uid":202383,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:50:38.000Z","msg":"所以話外國唔熟國情<br />\n<br />\n林鄭過到呢關 就算唔連任 上去都升官發大財啦"},{"pid":"fc119a2a7e8273565da196f6cf82e32752e1c2bc","tid":1198642,"uid":52939,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d4cb143c1e90f9cefcd1c0c9fc26440a8f006fae","tid":1198642,"uid":202383,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:50:38.000Z","msg":"所以話外國唔熟國情<br />\n<br />\n林鄭過到呢關 就算唔連任 上去都升官發大財啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:51: